<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Nginx - Single Mode</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 40px;
            background: #f9f9f9;
            color: #333;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #005f99;
        }
        .box {
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            background: white;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            max-width: 600px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="box">
        <h1>Nginx is Running in Single Mode</h1>
        <p>This page is being served directly by <strong>Nginx</strong>.</p>
        <p>In this mode, Apache is disabled and all traffic is handled only by Nginx.</p>
        <p><em>No reverse proxy behavior is active.</em></p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
